    @{" blockmon.dilp " link BLOCKMON} Block Monitor
    @{" poly.dilp     " link POLY} Polymorphic cipher

@endnode

@node AES "DIL · aes.dilp"

AES cipher
==========
  Intervene  : Yes
  Need seed  : Yes
  Description: This plugin encrypt's the data using AES256.
  Limits     : None

@endnode

@node DEFAULT "DIL · default.dilp"

Default plugin
==============
  Intervene  : No
  Need seed  : No
  Description: This plugin is used as default, it does nothing,
               just forwards the data.
  Limits     : None

@endnode

@node BLOCKMON "DIL · blockmon.dilp"

Block Monitor
=============
  Intervene  : No
  Need seed  : No
  Description: This plugin is used to monitor the access from the loaded
               filesystem.
  Limits     : Only surface 0 is shown.

@endnode

@node POLY "DIL · poly.dilp"

Polymorphic cipher
==================
  Intervene  : Yes
  Need seed  : Yes
  Description: This plugin encrypt's the data using a polymorphic function.
               The strength depends on the used blocksize and can be from
               4096 to 262144 bits.
  Limits     : None

@endnode


